    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014totally spotless and drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re gonna love it! \u2728",
